note.text: BYU QB Taysom Hill became 2nd QB in 2014 to have 200 yards
passing and more than 150 yards rushing in same game. Hill
also passed 2000 yards rushing and 4000 yards passing in his
career-1 of 14 QBs in NCAA history to do so before Sr. year
